{"word":"Bullock, or Ox","slug":"bullock,-or-ox","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Bullock, or Ox</b> Uses of:<br/> - For sacrifice<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=3'>Exo 29:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=14'>Exo 29:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=36'>Exo 29:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=4&verse=8'>Lev 4:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=4&verse=16'>Lev 4:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=7&verse=88'>Num 7:88</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=28&verse=31'>Num 28:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=29'>Num 29</a> <br/> - For plowing<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=14'>1Sa 14:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=19'>1Ki 19:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=14&verse=4'>Pro 14:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=32&verse=20'>Isa 32:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=31&verse=18'>Jer 31:18</a> <br/> - For treading out corn<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=25&verse=4'>Deu 25:4</a> <br/> - With wagons<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=7&verse=8'>Num 7:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=6&verse=6'>2Sa 6:6</a> <br/> Laws concerning:<br/> - Trespass by<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=21&verse=36'>Exo 21:36</a> <br/> - Theft of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=22&verse=10'>Exo 22:10</a> <br/> - Rest for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=12'>Exo 23:12</a> <br/> - Not to be muzzled, when treading grain<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=25&verse=4'>Deu 25:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=9&verse=9'>1Co 9:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=5&verse=18'>1Ti 5:18</a> <br/> - Not to be yoked with an ass<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=10'>Deu 22:10</a> <br/> Twelve brazen, under the molten sea in Solomon's temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=25'>1Ki 7:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=4&verse=4'>2Ch 4:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=52&verse=20'>Jer 52:20</a><br/><a href='S:Bull'>Bull</a>; <a href='S:Cattle'>Cattle</a><br/> Symbolic<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=1&verse=10'>Eze 1:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=4&verse=7'>Rev 4:7</a>"}]}